sourcesContent: import React from 'react' import Grid from '@material-ui/core/Grid'; import Card from '@material-ui/core/Card' import CardContent from '@material-ui/core/CardContent'; import CardActions from '@material-ui/core/CardActionArea'; import Typography from '@material-ui/core/Typography'; import Button from '@material-ui/core/Button'; import Moment from 'moment' const StudentHome = props=>{ let toDoArr; let closedArr; if(props.toGrade.length>0){ toDoArr=props.toGrade.map((e,i)=>( props.openModal(i)}> {e.name} Team: {e.team} Assessment: {e.assessment} Overall Grade: {e.overallGrade}/5 Click to Grade )) } if(props.toGrade.length===0){ toDoArr=( No Assessments in the to grade! ) } if(props.closedArr.length>0){ closedArr=props.closedArr.map((e,i)=>( {e.name} Due date: {Moment(e.dueDate).format('MMMM Do YYYY')} Class Overall: {e.overAll}/5 )) } if(props.closedArr.length===0){ closedArr=props.closedArr.map(e=>( No Assessments )) } return( To Grade {toDoArr} All Assessments {closedArr} ) } export default StudentHome
